      • addContextPanelFactory

        public void addContextPanelFactory(ContextPanelFactory contextPanelFactory)
        Adds the given ContextPanelFactory to the view hook, to be later added to the View.

        By default, the ContextPanelFactorys added are removed from the View when the extension is unloaded.

        Parameters:
        contextPanelFactory - the ContextPanelFactory that will be added to the View
        Since:
        2.5.0

      • addMainToolBarComponent

        public void addMainToolBarComponent(Component component)
        Adds the given Component (usually JButton, JToggleButton, JToolBar.Separator) to the view hook, to be later added to the main tool bar panel.

        By default, the Components added are removed from the main tool bar panel when the extension is unloaded.

        Parameters:
        component - the component that will be added to the main tool bar panel
        Since:
        2.6.0
        See Also:
        MainToolbarPanel.addToolBarComponent(Component), MainToolbarPanel.removeToolBarComponent(Component)
